[4] Henan
Date: Fri 9 Jun 2017 17:32 PM
Source: FIC (Flu Information Centre/Flu in China) [edited]
http://www.flu.org.cn/en/news_detail?action=ql&uid=&pd=&newsId=19503


Henan province reported 2 human H7N9 AIV cases (one in Nanyang city, one in Zhoukou city) between [3-9 Jun 2017].

The 48-year-old male patient, is a resident of Tanghe county of Nanyang city. He was in serious condition and remained in hospital for treatment.

The 41-year-old male patient, a resident of Dancheng county of Zhoukou city, was in serious condition and remained in hospital for treatment.

